'''logiX''', also known as '''logiX e.V.''', is a German eSports organization. Along with a League of Legends team, they also sponsor teams and players for Counterstrike: Source, Counterstrike 1.6, FIFA, StarCraft 2, Battlefield 3, Call of Duty 4, and Racing games.

